Davido’s Public Relations Officer, Aladegbola Oluwasegun, aka IamDre has said that working with the DMW Boss, Davido is a blessing. The PR officer made this known in a recent chat with The Nation saying, “First of all David is selfless, he puts his people first, it makes work easier, David is the type of person to give you his shirt and walk naked, working with David is a blessing, he knows when to make the right moves and decisions, always punctual to his gigs, always carrying everyone along, working with David has really upgraded my Work and Personality, lastly working with David is stress-free.”   Abudu: I won’t welcome insults, abuse     The Doctors Nigeria show partners Landmark to vaccinate show…     Sean Dampte waxes stronger as Hide Your Girls release draws…   Revealing how he met the superstar, he said “I met Davido while promoting his music way back in my university days, I used to do a lot of promotions for him back then in the University of Lagos, even before I met him physically. The first official meeting was at his house in Lekki Lagos, so when I graduated from the university we did more work from then and even got involved in his logistics team bringing my impact to the movement.” Continuing, Aladegbola said, “David is such a special soul that loves humans in general. When the energy connect he loves you unconditionally, I started getting closer and familiar with the crew then when my friend Eric DMW used to have me link up with the team sometimes when they are outside, from there I started getting familiar with the team and I became friends with everybody on the crew one after the other and friends turn family.”